## awkコマンド
```sh
# $0は行全てを表す
$ awk '{print $0}' access.log
```

```
# 結果
66.249.73.135 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
66.249.73.135 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
66.249.73.135 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
66.249.73.135 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
11.111.11.111 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
22.222.22.222 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
66.249.73.135 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
66.249.73.135 - - [20/May/2015:21:05:11 +0
```



```sh
$ awk '{print $1}' access.log
```
